snippet.title: Scala Toronto
snippet.description: Published talks delivered to the Scala Toronto (scalator) meetup.  Scala Toronto (https://www.meetup.com/scalator/) Scala Toronto is a great place to learn about the Scala (http://www.scala-lang.org/) language, libraries, the JVM, Akka, and Data Engineering topics. We also promote about related progressive technologies and ideas! All skill levels are welcome.
